           12 FILLER                   PIC X(049) VALUE SPACE.
           12 FILLER                   PIC X(005) VALUE "Page:".
           12 FILLER                   PIC X(001) VALUE SPACE.
           12 R1-HDR-Page-Count        PIC ZZ9.

