           12 FILLER   PIC X(006) VALUE SPACES.
           12 FILLER   PIC X(004) VALUE "Date".
           12 FILLER   PIC X(011) VALUE SPACES.
           12 FILLER   PIC X(006) VALUE "Salary".
           12 FILLER   PIC X(011) VALUE SPACES.
           12 FILLER   PIC X(005) VALUE "Bonus".
           12 FILLER   PIC X(005) VALUE SPACES.
